{"ts": "2026-06-09T22:03:21.936133+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:SmCO9G | {\"issues\":[{\"number\":6,\"title\":\"Update the safe scan profile\",\"body\":\"## Problem\\n\\nAdjust the safe local scan profile to include service/version detection while keeping scope restricted to localhost.\\n\\n## Expected areas to review\\n\\n- `scan_profiles/safe_local.yml`\\n- `scripts/run_safe_scan.sh`\\n\\n## Acceptance criteria\\n\\n- The requested change is implemented in the project files.\\n- Existing validation commands continue to pass.\\n- The change stays focused on the documented maintenance request.\",\"state\":\"OPEN\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"jhzheng0406\"},\"comments\":1,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-24T21:40:56Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-24T21:40:57Z\"},{\"number\":3,\"title\":\"Add localhost target inventory\",\"body\":\"## Problem\\n\\nUpdate the local Nmap target inventory so it documents the authorized localhost target and its expected service purpose.\\n\\n## Expected areas to review\\n\\n- `scan_targets/local_targets.txt`\\n- `docs/target_inventory.md`\\n\\n## Acceptance criteria\\n\\n- The requested change is implemented in the project files.\\n- Existing validation commands continue to pass.\\n- The change stays focused on the documented maintenance request.\",\"state\":\"OPEN\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"jhzheng0406\"},\"comments\":1,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-24T21:40:48Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-24T21:40:49Z\"},{\"number\":1,\"title\":\"Create a scan report from sample output\",\"body\":\"## Problem\\n\\nUse the sample Nmap XML output to produce a concise Markdown scan report under reports/.\\n\\n## Expected areas to review\\n\\n- `sample_data/nmap_localhost.xml`\\n- `scripts/nmap_xml_to_markdown.py`\\n- `reports/local_scan_report.md`\\n\\n## Acceptance criteria\\n\\n- The requested change is implemented in the project files.\\n- Existing validation commands continue to pass.\\n- The change stays focused on the documented maintenance request.\",\"state\":\"OPEN\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"jhzheng0406\"},\"comments\":1,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-24T21:40:42Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-24T21:40:43Z\"}],\"totalCount\":3,\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":false,\"hasPreviousPage\":false,\"startCursor\":\"Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyNi0wNS0yNFQyMTo0MDo1NlrPAAAAAQz-yHk=\",\"endCursor\":\"Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyNi0wNS0yNFQyMTo0MDo0MlrPAAAAAQz-xjc=\"}}", "id": "lc_0af9d770-04c2-4038-902a-37e24132c034"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "list_issues", "id": "d12fee25-4ed0-400f-acaf-55e953f28213", "tool_call_id": "call_61825e3a59974f61a66a898f", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
