{"ts": "2026-06-09T22:03:34.554603+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:SmCO9G | successfully downloaded text file (SHA: a6d7d272b38a70520d408affd2cded2f37e26c8c)", "id": "lc_f6372659-d636-4485-af99-d8a647968e81"}, {"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:SmCO9G | # Local Service Audit Toolkit\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | A small toolkit for maintaining an inventory of local development services and converting authorized Nmap XML output into readable reports.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | ## Project layout\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | - `scan_targets/` — Allowed local targets for service inventory.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | - `scan_profiles/` — Nmap scan profiles constrained to localhost and loopback targets.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | - `sample_data/` — Sample XML outputs used for parser development.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | - `reports/` — Generated Markdown and JSON reports.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | - `scripts/` — Report conversion and local scan helpers.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | ## Quick start\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | ```bash\n| MCP:SmCO9G | make validate\n| MCP:SmCO9G | ```\n| MCP:SmCO9G | ```bash\n| MCP:SmCO9G | python3 scripts/nmap_xml_to_markdown.py\n| MCP:SmCO9G | ```\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | ## Local scan workflow\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | 1. Keep approved targets in `scan_targets/local_targets.txt`.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | 2. Maintain scan options in `scan_profiles/safe_local.yml`.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | 3. Store parser fixtures in `sample_data/`.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | 4. Generate reports into `reports/`.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | The included scan helper refuses non-local targets by design.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | ## Maintenance notes\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | The helper scan script only accepts localhost or 127.0.0.1 targets.\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | ## Contributing\n| MCP:SmCO9G | \n| MCP:SmCO9G | Keep changes focused, update documentation when behavior changes, and run the v